product.name: Age group
product.description: Defines the target age range for a product, such as adults or kids

product.name: Target gender
product.description: Identifies the intended gender for a product, such as female, male or unisex

product.name: Color
product.description: Defines the primary color or pattern, such as blue or striped

product.name: Pants length type
product.description: Used to defines the length of pants, such as cropped or long

product.name: Fabric
product.description: Identifies the type of fabric used in a product, for example, cotton or denim

product.name: Sneaker style
product.description: Identifies the design or type of sneakers, such as athletic or high-top

product.name: Dress style
product.description: Identifies the design of a dress, such as wrap or empire waist

product.name: Closure type
product.description: Defines the method used to fasten or secure a product, such as zipper or buckles

product.name: Sandal style
product.description: Specifies the style of sandals, such as ankle strap or lace-up

product.name: Heel height type
product.description: Defines the height of a shoe's heel, such as flat or high

product.name: Size
product.description: Used to specify the size of a product, such as 0-3 months or Extra large (XL)

product.name: Dress occasion
product.description: Specifies the intended occasion for a dress, e.g. holiday, everyday

product.name: Shoe size
product.description: Used to define the size of footwear, e.g. Extra large (XL), 9.5

product.name: Clothing features
product.description: Describes unique properties of apparel, such as water resistant or wrinkle resistant

product.name: Fit
product.description: Describes the fit of a garment, typically pant shape; e.g. skinny leg, wide

product.name: Waist rise
product.description: Indicates where on the waist a garment sits, like low, medium or high

product.name: Shoe fit
product.description: Defines the width of footwear, such as narrow or wide

product.name: Watch display
product.description: Distinguishes between watch displays, such as digital or analog

product.name: Band color
product.description: Specifies the color of a watch band, e.g. multicolor, rose gold

product.name: Watch material
product.description: Specifies the type of material used for the watch, such as titanium or silicone

product.name: Watch features
product.description: Identifies special characteristics of a watch, such as automatic movement or luminous hands

product.name: Bag/Case closure
product.description: Identifies the type of closure used on bags or cases, e.g. key lock, velcro

product.name: Carry options
product.description: Specifies the carrying methods available for items, such as a handle or shoulder strap

product.name: Care instructions
product.description: Provides guidance for product upkeep, such as hand wash or dry clean only

product.name: Bag/Case material
product.description: Identifies the main material used in a bag or case, such as leather or canvas

product.name: Bag/Case features
product.description: Describes the unique characteristics of a bag or case, like waterproof or lightweight

product.name: Bag/Case storage features
product.description: Identifies unique storage elements in bags or cases, such as adjustable dividers or external pockets
